sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform UI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(opendatahub namespace)
    participant JobSetAPI as JobSet API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant Master as Training Pod 0 (Master)<br/>29500/TCP TCP
    participant Workers as Training Pods 1..N (Workers)<br/>29500/TCP TCP
    participant Progression as RHAI Progression Tracker

    Note over User,Workers: Flow 1: TrainJob Submission and Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (RBAC)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Resolve TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>JobSetAPI: Create JobSet CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (per-TrainJob)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup (if gang-scheduling)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create batch Jobs + Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Master->>Workers: NCCL/gRPC distributed training<br/>29500/TCP plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy restricted)
    Workers-->>Master: Gradient synchronization

    Note over Controller,Master: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking

    loop Every 30s (configurable 5s-300s)
        Progression->>Master: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy restricted)
        Master-->>Progression: JSON metrics<br/>(progressPercentage, currentStep,<br/>totalSteps, currentEpoch)
        Progression->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over Progression,Master: On job complete/fail
    Progression->>Master: Read pod termination message<br/>(final metrics capture)
